Section: admin

Package: singularity-wrapper
Architecture: all
Depends:
 ${shlibs:Depends},
 ${misc:Depends},
 build-essential,
 debhelper,
 debootstrap,
 python3,
 python3-apt,
 python3-distutils-extra,
 python3-jinja2,
 singularity-container (>= 2.4),
 squashfs-tools
Description: Create and build wrapper packages around singularity images
 This package provides a script that permits to create packages that provides
 a wrapper around a singularity image with a specific package inside.
 The script can also be used inside the package to re-generate the singularity
 image.
